timeline.bodyText:
A DefaultByteBufHolder interface may help to reduce some of the duplicated code for the different impls of of ByteBufHolder. Something like:
interface DefaultByteBufHolder<T extends ByteBufHolder> extends ByteBufHolder {

  @Override
  T replace(ByteBuf content);

  @Override
  default T copy() {
    return replace(content().copy());
  }

  // ...

  @Override
  default int refCnt() {
    return content().refCnt();
  }

  // ...
}

